WEBVTT

00:03:28.048 --> 00:03:32.975
scale them up to global giants
by the time they get to 30,

00:03:32.999 --> 00:03:36.454
and yet, we expect
these young digital leaders

00:03:36.478 --> 00:03:41.611
to somehow miraculously embody
the relationship wisdoms

00:03:41.635 --> 00:03:44.588
we older workers
have had decades to learn.

00:03:45.125 --> 00:03:48.800
It's hard to microwave
your emotional intelligence.

00:03:49.689 --> 00:03:55.427
There's ample evidence that gender-
and ethnically diverse companies

00:03:55.451 --> 00:03:56.811
are more effective.

00:03:57.426 --> 00:03:58.682
But what about age?

